The paper deals with topology inference from data, which is a problem in computational geometry (cs.CG) and data structures (cs.DS). The approach involves sparsification of data, which is a common technique in numerical analysis (cs.NA). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning techniques for topology inference, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper mentions the application of the approach to image data, which is a problem in computer vision (cs.CV).
